## 2. LiNKsites Pricing Analysis and Final Decisions

## 2.1 Operating and Infrastructure Model Used for Pricing

- LiNKsites runs template-first, multi-tenant architecture.
- Control plane runs centralized services (CMS and related core services).
- Shared frontend runtime serves multiple customers per droplet.
- Enterprise uses dedicated frontend isolation.
- Supabase is shared in the early stage as part of the multi-line stack.
- Pricing is set to stay materially cheaper than typical managed alternatives while protecting margin.

